y partisan strife until the last decade of the Empire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aAgriculturezBrazilzGoiás (State)xHistoryy19th century. 4aHistory -- Latin American. 7aHISTORY / Latin America / South America.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780804767743zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804767743423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804767743/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles